response.overview: Earth's sexiest Super XXX Hero is a young co-ed from another planet. Supergirl (Alamah Rae) barely escapes the destruction of her home planet, but her greatest challenge lies ahead - sorority life! With the help of her cousin, Superman (Dale Dabone) and her bff, Barbara Gordon (Sunny Lane), Supergirl tries to pass off as human. The only thing standing in her way from a a life of text books, parties and casual sex, is Natasha Luthor (Andy San Dimas), the Queen Bitch of the Tri-Pi Sorority. In Luthor's plan for world domination, Supergirl is the last piece of the puzzle.
response.title: Batgirl V Supergirl
